item.title: Project 1: Learn Two Digit Numbers
item.description: Created an application to draw two digit number and learn its word form.The model is trained locally on browser using tensorflow.js.Data used for training model is loaded in the form of Sprite sheet to optimise pre-training time.Cnn model is built to detect the integers drawn on canvas.Build this application for childern under the age of 5 years to teach them two digit numbers.

item.title: Project 2: BSE Anomaly Detection
item.description: In the project, I built an outlier detection in the BSE index project between 1991-2019. This could be useful for someone new to the BSE market and don't know about 7 common anomalies. They could take a look at the graphs and find the convergence with the events in history.
